name: historical-north-atlantic-tropical-cyclone-tracks-1851-2005-geographic-nad83-noaa-2006-atl-2006
notes: This Historical North Atlantic Tropical Cyclone Tracks file contains the 6-hourly (0000, 0600, 1200, 1800 UTC) center locations and intensities for all subtropical depressions and storms, extratropical storms, tropical lows, waves, disturbances, depressions and storms, and all hurricanes, from 1851 through 2005.
